description: Deletes the specified instance profile. The instance profile must not have an associated role. For more information about instance profiles, see Using instance profiles in the IAM User Guide.

parameters.name: InstanceProfileName
parameters.description: The name of the instance profile to delete. This parameter allows (through its regex pattern) a string of characters consisting of upper and lowercase alphanumeric characters with no spaces. You can also include any of the following characters: _+=,.@-
